      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3 in concours-ready condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains factory-spec with documented subframe reinforcement and a fully serviced VANOS system, ensuring peak mechanical synchronization. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component reflects a zero-compromise maintenance philosophy. The limited-slip variable M differential provides surgical torque vectoring, while the exterior retains its original deep-luster finish. This is a blue-chip investment for the purist seeking a mechanically flawless, high-revving masterpiece.",
